Package com.toldcalculator.android.tc.model.entity

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Aircraft
    This entity class holds the basic information about the aircraft such as the name, the aircraft type, and the aircraft's basic empty weight.
    Airport
    This entity class is used to hold basic airport information such as the airport name, ICAO identifier, and elevation.
    Runway
    This entity class holds information about a runway for a specific airport such as the airport id, runway identifier, length, and width.
    SavedTakeoffData
    This entity class holds takeoff data, aircraft information, and weather information.
    TakeoffData
    This entity class is used to hold takeoff data based on altitude, weight, and temperature.
    TakeoffPowerN1
    This entity class hold a single N1 power setting based off temperature and altitude.
    User
    This entity class is used to store user information such as the user name, default aircraft and airport.
    Weather
    This entity class is used to hold basic metar weather information.
